										Equipment Platforms										








Equipment Platforms
lwolfe63




FCP designs custom support platforms for a wide variety of unique applications. No matter the size and shape of your particular equipment, FCP can design the right equipment platforms to support it. From Entertainment and Defense to Manufacturing and Retail, FCP has the experience to design a system that’s just right for your needs.
To maximize useable floor space, our equipment support platforms are designed to fit around any existing obstructions and can accommodate stairways and access locations as needed. Our System Designers will create industrial structures to meet your specific load and conveyor platform requirements, whether it is for storage, material handling equipment or concentrated loads of heavy equipment.
The unique design of FCP Free-Space Mezzanines ™ also allows for fast installation, future expansion and can be dismantled and re-assembled if required. We’ve even designed support platforms with rollers and air jacks.



 
